Body:
Description: AIC Console error message after database migration.

Stealthaudit database has been migrated to a new SQL server. The storage settings have been updated to the new SQL server. Now the web portal access tab is throwing an error message.

"Unable to contact the SQL server database"
Next Steps Updated: Awaiting meeting to live troubelshoot.
What We've Learned Updated: Customer doesn't seem to be able to locate or access AIC.
What We've Learned Updated: AIC was not modified to use the new database. We fixed the database to point at the new location and the issue is resolved.
